        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Multiple Failures</title>
            <para>In the event that multiple failures occur, the dash lamp will react as it normally would during a
                single failure, and the LEDs will show one failure at a time. When the first condition is fixed and the
                system is reset, the next condition area will appear at the LEDs. This way, the driver or mechanic does
                not lose track of condition areas, and the system is not restored until each and every error is
                corrected and the EC-16 is reset.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
